item.title: Weekly Review #64 - Life Is Here (Stoner and Normal People)
item.description: 'Photograph - Ed Sheeran' Preface This piece is a reflection on life from July 1st to July 9th, 2024. This week, I maintained an early rising routine for several days, dedicating time to reading and studying with high efficiency. However, establishing a regular pattern still requires time and adjustment. I’m also exploring how to enter and switch work modes more swiftly. I’m simultaneously reading several books: “Atlas Shrugged”, “Normal People”, and “What My Bones Know”.
